    <tr>
      <td colspan="13">Financial Data:</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td colspan="13" style="padding-left:5px;">- Presented and calculated from the consolidated statement and displayed as cumulative quarterly statement by fiscal year (Company statement will be presented and calculated incase consolidated statement is not available.)</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td colspan="13" style="padding-left:5px;">- In case that the listed companies restate the financial statement, financial data from the restatement will be calculated and displayed instead of original statement. Adjustment Status wil be also displayed.</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td colspan="13" style="padding-left:5px;">- Information on the financial statements is presented according to the information that the listed companies submit on that period. The investors should study additional information from the companies' financial statements.</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td colspan="13" style="padding-left:5px;">- Restatement (R) means companies may restate or reclassify their financial statements. For more detail, please go to Financial Statement screen.</td>
